{"tid":1831718,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"穆迪三年內第二度調低香港主權評級　「香港管治能力遜預期」","createTime":"2020-01-20T14:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T15:11:27.000Z","uid":343294,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d4995a47972dda8dccc3ffe1bbf85f2b7839c053","tid":1831718,"uid":343294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T14:59:00.000Z","msg":"國際評級機構穆迪（Moody's）將香港政府長期信貸評級下調至Aa3，評級展望調整為穩定。<br />\n<br />\n穆迪早在2017年5月曾下調香港評級，當時由Aa1 降至Aa2。<br />\n<br />\n其他評級機構方面，惠譽（Fitch Ratings）去年9月已將香港信用評級由第二高的AA+，下調至AA級，評級展望評為負面。標準普爾（Standard &amp; Poor's）就在2017年9月下調香港評級。<br />\n<br />\n穆迪在報告首先指出，香港體制和管治能力不及以往所估計。該行指出，過去9個月香港沒有展現具體計劃處理香港市民所反映的政治、經濟以及社會問題，認為其管治能力不如該行早前所評估，也可能是香港特區自治較該行原有估計有更大限制。<br />\n<br />\n穆迪目前給予香港Aa3評級和穩定展望，該行解釋，預期香港即使在政治和社會不明朗下，經濟陷衰退壓力，香港仍保持財政實力和宏觀經濟穩定。<br />\n<br />\n該行補充，即使不及預先估計強勁，香港體制和管治能力仍較中國為好，令香港評級較中國仍高出一級。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2546722?r=mcsdfb2&amp;fbclid=IwAR0x07u39S0kma5AgIbji_cfjdaJGjQVNIalYIlO_P7y8o-WbWUAsUzrwGA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2546722%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb2%26fbclid%3DIwAR0x07u39S0kma5AgIbji_cfjdaJGjQVNIalYIlO_P7y8o-WbWUAsUzrwGA&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9%2FFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=f23d7231\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2546722?r=mcsdfb2&amp;fbclid=IwAR0x07u39S0kma5AgIbji_cfjdaJGjQVNIalYIlO_P7y8o-WbWUAsUzrwGA</a>"},{"pid":"edb4b253434e5473bd65e61c044552dde085e9d9","tid":1831718,"uid":343294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T14:59:45.000Z","msg":"攬炒中"},{"pid":"583c80f796d5aa5594c97513f5e037ff9430fe4a","tid":1831718,"uid":118888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:00:50.000Z","msg":"咁撚慢<br />\n比外資慢慢走？"},{"pid":"9267805b6538995306ea6aaf65305b9068fc2f27","tid":1831718,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:02:56.000Z","msg":"想問最低咪level?<br />\n快啲跌 唔好比支那用香港吸血"},{"pid":"bb650badf6afdfd2b988f75194da8822d5c2ca4b","tid":1831718,"uid":136645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:03:16.000Z","msg":"武則天好廢，煮飯啦"},{"pid":"3ebaaf36d9f33a87325ec708eccd3a40bf354a76","tid":1831718,"uid":343294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9267805b6538995306ea6aaf65305b9068fc2f27","tid":1831718,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:02:56.000Z","msg":"想問最低咪level?<br />\n快啲跌 唔好比支那用香港吸血"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"not yet, 中國依家Moody's rank 緊Aa3, 香港Aa2依然高一個 notch，我諗中國經濟下行，內憂外忠，慢慢social unrest，管治能力下降，都差唔多到中國downgrade。"}]}